DESCRIPTION:[Podcast: Let's Talk ID] Duration: 1698\n\nIDSA CEO Jeanne Mar
 razzo\, MD\, MPH\, FIDSA\, hosts IDSA board members Ronald Nahass\, MD\, M
 HCM\, FIDSA\, Wendy Armstrong\, MD\, FIDSA\, and Max Brito\, MD\, MPH\, FI
 DSA\, to discuss the challenges and opportunities shaping the field of inf
 ectious diseases. From defending vaccine science to strengthening the ID w
 orkforce and growing membership\, the group shares how IDSA is responding 
 to today’s health care challenges and preparing for the future.\n\nEvent
  URL: https://www.buzzsprout.com/2019912/episodes/19110518-advocacy-workfo
