SUMMARY:CFAR Seminar with Dr. Vincent Marconi - June 4\, 2026
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260604T230000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260605T000000
DTSTAMP:20260516T064814Z
UID:457a3456a85804c6@gid-seminars.wnprc.wisc.edu
CATEGORIES:Fred Hutch Center for AIDS Research (CFAR)
DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nOnline Meeting Link: https:/
 /washington.zoom.us/meeting/register/hxWUcWKBTii-wAvaS382eg\nAccessibility
  Contact: cfar@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Lectures/Seminars\n\nREGISTER NOW!\nRe
 gister via this link for virtual attendance\nzoom registration: \nhttps://
 washington.zoom.us/meeting/register/hxWUcWKBTii-wAvaS382eg\n--------------
 ------------------------------------------------------------------\n4:00pm
  - 5:00pm\nVIRTUAL\nCFAR Seminar Speaker: Vincent Marconi\, MD\nAging from
  Infection: Is there a Fountain of Youth?\n\nDr. Vincent Marconi is the Di
 rector of the Infectious Diseases Research Program at the Atlanta VA Medic
 al Center and a Professor of Medicine in the Division of Infectious Diseas
 es\, Department of Medicine\, Emory University School of Medicine and join
 tly a Professor of Global Health in the Rollins School of Public Health an
 d the Emory Vaccine Center\, Emory University. He has extensive experience
  as a PI of multiple NIH R and U grants and VA Merit awards as well as a m
 entor and investigator on numerous NIH\, CDC\, VA and industry-sponsored m
 ulti-site domestic and international clinical and translational trials for
  people with HIV and COVID-19. He is the Director of the Emory CFAR Data S
 cience Core and has served on multiple national and international research
  and steering committees. His research focus areas are (1) to elucidate th
 e role of viral infections in the aging process\, (2) to study the impact 
 of anti-inflammatory interventions on age-related outcomes and viral reser
 voirs\, and (3) to utilize implementation science for improving treatment 
 and care for people with HIV and Long COVID.\n\nEvent URL: https://washing
 ton.zoom.us/meeting/register/hxWUcWKBTii-wAvaS382eg\n\nSource: uw_cfar
LOCATION:Zoom
URL:https://washington.zoom.us/meeting/register/hxWUcWKBTii-wAvaS382eg
